com.rabbitmq.http.client

Class ReactorNettyClientOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rabbitmq.http.client.ReactorNettyClientOptions

  • public class ReactorNettyClientOptions
extends java.lang.Object
    Options for ReactorNettyClient. An instance of this class can be passed in to ReactorNettyClient constructor for settings like Jackson JSON object mapper, authentication, TLS, error handling.
    Since:
    2.1.0
    See Also:
    ReactorNettyClient
